#Dataset
The dataset used in this project contains supermarket sales transaction data, including:

- Invoice ID
- Branch
- City
- Customer Type
- Gender
- Product Line
- Unit Price
- Quantity
- Tax 5%
- Total Revenue
- Date & Time
- Payment Method
- COGS
- Gross Margin Percentage
- Gross Income
- Rating

Dataset is used for:
- Sales analysis
- Profit analysis
- Customer behavior analysis
- Product performance tracking
- Payment trend visualization
